        "jsCode": "const data = items[0].json;\n\n// 1️⃣ If AI Agent output exists\nif (data.output) {\n  return [{\n    json: {\n      reply: data.output.trim()\n    }\n  }];\n}\n\n// 2️⃣ If Location branch output exists\nif (data.whatsappMessage) {\n  return [{\n    json: {\n      reply: data.whatsappMessage.trim()\n    }\n  }];\n}\n\n// 3️⃣ Fallback response\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    reply: \"Sorry, I couldn't process your request.\"\n  }\n}];\n\n"
